Given I am logged in Radio Report application
And I am on Page 3 of Cranial MRT 
And I select 'Yes' in Contrast enhanced tab
Then I go to Page 9
And 'Medium interhemispheric slit, regular width of the inner
and outer CSF spaces, no CSF circulation disturbance' radio button is enabled 
And 'No details' radio button is enabled 
And 'Finding' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Finding' radio button 
Then dropdown below is enabled 

When I select 'Ventricle configuration' from the dropdown 
And I select 'Differential diagnosis' tab 
Then 'Differential diagnosis 1 *' dropdown is enabled 

When I select 'Internal hydrocephalus' from 'Differential diagnosis 1 *' dropdown
Then 'Suspicion of' checkbox is enabled 
And 'Differential diagnosis 2' dropdown is enabled 

When I select 'Suspicion of' checkbox
Then checkbox is selected 

When I select 'External hydrocephalus' from 'Differential diagnosis 2' dropdown
Then 'Subordinate' checkbox is enabled 

When I select 'Subordinate' checkbox
Then checkbox is selected 
